Filename: mcmonitor.c
Author: Joseph d'Eon
Description:
  A daemon that watches for minecraft-pi to be run. When it is run, it loads 
  the minecraftModChooser (see its functionality in minecraftModChooser README
  in /home/pi/ModChooser). When minecraft is no longer running. This daemon
  makes sure the modChooser is no longer running as well.

Usage:
  This daemon will run on boot. If killed, run with sudo ./mcmonitor. If
  changed: gcc -o mcmonitor mcmonitor.c to compile, then run.
